flowchart LR
    U[User] -->|Interacts with| CE[Chrome Extension UI]

    subgraph Extension[Browser Extension Layer]
        CE --> AC[Authentication Screen]
        CE --> MV[Main Vault Interface]
        MV --> ADD[Add Password Tab]
        MV --> LIST[Passwords Tab]
        MV --> GEN[Password Generator Tab]
        CE --> CRYPTO[Client-side AES-256-GCM Encryption]
        CE --> STORE[Local Storage for Session Data]
    end

    AC -->|Register and Login| API
    ADD -->|Submit encrypted credentials| API
    LIST -->|Fetch encrypted credentials| API

    CRYPTO -->|Encrypt before sending| API
    API -->|JSON responses and JWT| CE

    subgraph Backend[Local Backend Server Layer]
        API[Express REST API]
        AUTH[Auth Routes]
        CREDS[Credential Routes]
        MIDDLE[JWT Middleware]
        DBL[Database Access Layer]
    end

    API --> AUTH
    API --> CREDS
    AUTH --> MIDDLE
    CREDS --> MIDDLE
    CREDS --> DBL

    subgraph Data[Data Layer]
        SQLITE[(SQLite Database)]
        USERS[(users table)]
        CREDENTIALS[(credentials table)]
    end

    DBL --> SQLITE
    SQLITE --> USERS
    SQLITE --> CREDENTIALS
